<a name="509"><span style="display: none">CEPro@CES</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">CEPro@CES</div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/TechZones/CES_TZ_CEPro_200.jpg"/>
<p><em>CE Pro</em> Magazine is pulling out all the stops to create a destination for custom electronics integrators within CES. Hosting a comprehensive offering of the newest consumer electronics, home automation, lighting and shade control, energy management and retrofit (wireless) control and security devices, CEPro@CES is where professional residential and light commercial installers will gather. <a href="/Show-Floor/CES-TechZones.aspx">Check out this and other CES TechZones.</a></p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="511"><span style="display: none">Good Advice for International Travelers</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Good Advice for International Travelers</div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/International%20Pages/visa.gif"/>
<p>With 35,000 industry professionals from 150 countries expected to attend the 2013 show, it&rsquo;s best to start the process of obtaining your visa now! You&rsquo;ll need to register for the show, request your letter of invitation and make your appointment for a visa interview early. Wait times for a visa interview can be several weeks or more in many countries, especially during peak travel periods.<a href="/For-International-Visitors/Travel-Visa.aspx"> Find important visa related information here</a>.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
You can also <a href="/For-International-Visitors.aspx">learn more about the services we provide our international attendees</a>, tips for obtaining a visa and information about our delegation program. </p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="514"><span style="display: none">CES Hotels Now Accepting Reservations</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">CES Hotels Now Accepting Reservations</div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Hotel%20and%20Travel%20Images/Hotels/Strip_165x125.jpg"/>
<p>Book your room today and avoid the &ldquo;sold out&rdquo; signs. Visit <a href="/Hotel-Travel/Hotel-Reservations.aspx">CESweb.org/hotel</a> to book now! Remember, by staying at an official CES hotel, you&rsquo;ll have access to free CES shuttles between your hotel and the LVCC.</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="510"><span style="display: none">Taking the Monorail to the LVH or the LVCC?</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Taking the Monorail to the LVH or the LVCC?</div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Hotel%20and%20Travel%20Images/monorail_logo.gif"/>
<p>We can help! CES has partnered once again with the Las Vegas Monorail to bring you savings on select ticket types. <a href="https://tickets.lvmonorail.com/ces2013/" target="_blank">See CES&rsquo; special discount page</a> for info on how to purchase. It&rsquo;s never too early to purchase, as tickets expire one year from date of purchase.</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="512"><span style="display: none">CNET</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">CNET</div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Logos/CNET.gif"/>
<p>CNET, the<em> Official Digital News and Video Partner</em> of CES, will be live at the 2013 CES and once again delivering the most comprehensive coverage of the show. Dozens of expert editors will be reporting on keynotes, participating in SuperSessions, giving First Looks of the hot new products and canvassing the show floor to select who will be awarded the prestigious Best of CES award.<br />
<br />
Check out <a href="http://www.cnet.com/ces" target="_blank">www.cnet.com/ces</a> to see a full recap of the 2012 CES.</p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="515"><span style="display: none">Vote for Us!</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Vote for Us!</div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Logos/Award%20Logos/TSEaward.gif"/>
<p>Innovation drives the trade show industry. <strong><em>Trade Show Executive</em></strong> magazine&rsquo;s<em> <strong>10th Annual Innovation Awards | Readers&rsquo; Choice </strong></em>salutes those who make waves, defy tradition and create new value for show managers, exhibitors, attendees and the exposition industry as a whole.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
Please show your support for CES by voting for us in two categories: the &ldquo;Most Innovative Green Initiatives by Show Management&rdquo; and &ldquo;Most Innovative Organization in the Trade Show Industry&rdquo;. <a href="https://www.tradeshowexecutive.com/Ballot_request.asp" target="_blank">Retrieve your ballot </a>and share with your friends on Facebook and Twitter too. Voting is open until Wednesday, August 15. </p>
<br><br>
<hr class="separator">
<br>
<a name="513"><span style="display: none">In the Business of Health and Fitness Technology?</span></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">In the Business of Health and Fitness Technology?</div><br/>
<img style ='float: right; margin: 0 5px 5px 5px;' src="/cesweb/media/CESWeb/Logos/CEA%20Logos/CEAlogo.gif"/>
<p>Then join CEA&rsquo;s <strong>new</strong> Health and Fitness Technology Working Group to take advantage of promotional opportunities, access to research, networking and business development opportunities. The Health and Fitness Working Group works to raise awareness of consumer electronics devices and how they can help improve health and fitness.<br />
&nbsp;<br />
Get involved by participating in our satellite media tours, exhibiting at the FitnessTech TechZone at CES or helping develop market research studies. Not a CEA member? Visit<a href="http://www.ce.org/membership" target="_blank"> </a><a href="http://www.ce.org/membership/">CE.org/membership</a> for more information or contact <a href="mailto:JCutts@CE.org">Jack Cutts </a>at +1703-907-7052 to join.</p>
